oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jeannine Jasper at the Tennessee State Fair (Prop for Play It By Heart)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Metal photoplates; Musicals;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing Jeannine Jasper at the Tennessee State Fair on September 7, 1969. Poster features a metal photoplate of Jeannine Jasper. This poster was made for the musical Play It By Heart, during its run at the Human Race Theatre Company from June 12 to 29, with Trisha Rapier playing Jeannine Jasper.
